## Most Recent Changes

- Enabled persistent debug tooling and realtime store registration in `os/static/projects/sbn/app.js`, including REST snapshot bootstrap and `SBN_PWA_*` console helpers.
- Turned on Mishkah devtools auto-loading (`os/static/projects/sbn/index.html`, `os/static/lib/mishkah.js`) and exposed `MishkahStoreDebug`/`MishkahAppDebug` inspectors via `os/static/lib/mishkah.div.js`.
- Centralized realtime store/app registries inside `os/static/lib/mishkah.store.js` and `os/static/lib/mishkah.core.js` so every instance is discoverable from the console.
- Ensured the smart-store REST bootstrap uses `window.location.origin` and caches the initial fetch (`os/static/lib/mishkah.simple-store.js`), avoiding duplicate requests.
- Updated backend boot logic (`os/src/server.js`) to hydrate each moduleâ€™s table list dynamically from its schema fallback instead of hardcoding tables in `modules.json`.
